The quarterly meeting of Government College Ughelli Old Boys Association (GCUOBA) will hold in Lagos on Sunday. A statement issued by the President of the Lagos branch of GCUOBA, Mr. Sam Omatseye, said the meeting will take place at the secretariat of the association at No 22, McNeil Road, Yaba, Lagos at 2.30 pm. The meeting, the statement added, promises to be a fascinating time with all the old boys in Lagos. “Old boys of all generations, including the young and Ancient Mariners, have indicated interest to attend,” the statement added.